Important notes:
-----------------

1. The expressions i = i+1, i += 1, ++i and i++ are all same.
2. j = ++i; first increments i then assign the incremented value to j.
3. j = i++; first assign the current value of i to j then increment the i.
4. while(i++ < 10) first checks the conditions, then increments i.
5. while(++i < 10) first increments i then checks the conditions.
